                <div id="usageSupervision-notes" class="row">
                    <!-- Notes/Details -->
                    <div id="" class="col-4 response-cell"><p><b>What supervision system are you currently running?</b>
                            <br><%= usage_questions.supervision.supervision_system %></p></div>
                    <div id="" class="col-4 response-cell"><p><b>What are your current pain-points?</b>
                            <br><%= usage_questions.supervision.pain_points %></p></div>
                    <div id="" class="col-4 response-cell"><p><b>Are there deficiencies in your current process that put you at risk?</b>
                            <br><%= usage_questions.supervision.deficiencies %></p></div>
                    <div id="" class="col-4 response-cell"><p><b>What are the customer's lines of business that has different Supervision
                                requirements?</b>
                            <br><%= usage_questions.supervision.business_supervision_requirements %></p></div>
                    <div id="" class="col-4 response-cell"><p><b>Is review Centralized / De-centralized?</b>
                            <br><%= usage_questions.supervision.review %></p></div>
                    <div id="" class="col-4 response-cell"><p><b>What is the escalation process when issues / violations are found?</b>
